OL,3,CNew Bishop of Penrith appointed
OL,5,FThe new Bishop of Penrith has been
OL,6,Fappointed following approval by The
OL,7,FKing.
OL,9,FThe Reverend Canon Dr Michael John
OL,10,FLeyden takes on the role as successor
OL,11,Fto the Right Reverend Robert James
OL,12,FSaner-Haigh.
OL,14,FHe grew up in Merseyside and studied
OL,15,Fat Oxford University and Chester
OL,16,FUniversity and was trained for
OL,17,Fministry at St John's College in
OL,18,FNottingham.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
