PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773436320
OL,3,CNew Bishop of Penrith appointed
OL,5,FSpeaking to ITV Border, the said:
OL,6,F"There is no doubt that we live in
OL,7,Fturbulent times and there is no doubt
OL,8,Fthat we need a bit more love and a bit
OL,9,Fmore hope in the world.
OL,11,F"I am always struck by the fact that
OL,12,FJesus commands us to love one another
OL,13,Fand you might think why has that got
OL,14,Fto be a command, surely it is easy to
OL,15,Fdo.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773436320
OL,3,CNew Bishop of Penrith appointed
OL,5,F"You might look around and see that it
OL,6,Fis a job of discipline of learning to
OL,7,Flove others. I really hope as the
OL,8,Fchurch we can play our part across
OL,9,FCumbria in learning to love our
OL,10,Fcommunities."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
