OL,3,CNew Bishop of Penrith appointed
OL,5,FA statement from the Prime Minister's
OL,6,FOffice said: "The King has approved
OL,7,Fthe nomination of The Reverend Canon
OL,8,FDr Michael John Leyden BA, MA, MSt,
OL,9,FPhD, Dean and CEO of Emmanuel
OL,10,FTheological College, to the Suffragan
OL,11,FSee of Penrith, in the Diocese of
OL,12,FCarlisle, in succession to the Right
OL,13,FReverend Robert James Saner-Haigh, MA,
OL,14,FMPhil, following his translation to
OL,15,Fthe See of Carlisle."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
